OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith some sunshine on Thursday and
OL,7,FFriday but some cloud lingering along
OL,8,Fcoasts. Dry on Saturday but cloudier
OL,9,Fthan of late.
